\large e^A
A = \left( \begin{array}{ccc} 0 & a \\ 0 & 0  \end{array} \right)
\large e^A = \sum \limits_{k=0}^\infty \frac{1}{k!} A^k
\left( \begin{array}{ccc} 1 & 0 \\ 0 & 1  \end{array} \right) + \left( \begin{array}{ccc} 0 & a \\ 0 & 0  \end{array} \right) + \left( \begin{array}{ccc} 0 & 0 \\ 0 & 0  \end{array} \right) +    . . . 
\left( \begin{array}{ccc} 1 & a \\ 0 & 1  \end{array} \right)
